description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Dubrovnik, Croatia
-Ibiza, Spain
-Hvar, Croatia
-Santorini, Greece
-Palma de Mallorca, Spain
-Dead Sea, Israel
-Antalya, Turkey
-Ayia Napa, Cyprus
-Comino, Malta
-Tunis, Tunisia
name: Mediterranean Journey
